🚨 𝐁𝐑𝐄𝐀𝐊𝐈𝐍𝐆: Brazilian Federation, on a mission and confident to get Carlo Ancelotti 👀🇧🇷

The proposal as new head coach has been submitted with emissaries in Spain working to get it done soon.

Brazil respect Real Madrid decision timing… but they expect Ancelotti to 𝐥𝐞𝐚𝐯𝐞 the club as clear tendence.

❗️ Seleçao want Ancelotti to be ready for June, 𝐧𝐨𝐭 waiting until the end of the new FIFA Club World Cup.
